Adapted from http://grisha.org/blog/2013/05/31/simple-solution-to-password-reuse/
As seen on hacker news

this app in chrome web store:
https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/password-maker/ialikkbbdipamacdpjbjjffohcblhchp

A simple solution to not having the same password on every darn web service.

And without having to use some fancy-azz program like 1password.

This way you should be able to verify all the code yourself!

note that there is an android google play store version available:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.graehl.passwordmaker